data.enText: an extreme right-wing political system or attitude which is in favour of strong central government and which does not allow any opposition

tr: a political theory advocating an authoritarian hierarchical government (as opposed to democracy or liberalism)

value.def: Fascism is a set of right-wing political beliefs that includes strong control of society and the economy by the state, a powerful role for the armed forces, and the stopping of political opposition.
value.tran: 法西斯主义;军事独裁主义
